file: bmptk/tools/README

Bare Metal Programming Tool Kit tools directory

This directory contains various support tools for bmptk.

directories
   image_sizes    : tool to show sizes of various sections in an executable

files
   img_to_cpp.py  : Python tool that converts an image to .h and .cpp files
   lpc21.exe      : serial bootloader for philips LPC chips, slightly adapted
   README         : this file
   ttf_to_cpp.py  : Python tool that converts an font to .h and .cpp files
   txt_to_cpp.py  : Python tool that converts a text file to .h and .cpp files
   
   


